{"tid":159743,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"[低級問題]  吸塵","createTime":"2017-03-17T08:23:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T03:58:57.000Z","uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8ba5e0b975b181274b4c9fc0f06960243fce7323","tid":159743,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:23:15.000Z","msg":"其實有冇可能一邊擰下擰下個鏡頭，一邊用用吸塵機吸走入面d塵呢？<br />\n<br />\n但又要確保唔會有新既塵係鏡頭邊位入返去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗到腦已壞"},{"pid":"f161ce963b77270c3861f6ac5237e5b16cbf4b2d","tid":159743,"uid":54655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:47:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實有冇可能一邊擰下擰下個鏡頭，一邊用用吸塵機吸走入面d塵呢？<br />\n<br />\n但又要確保唔會有新既塵係鏡頭邊位入返去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗到腦已壞</blockquote><br />\n有無咁多塵呀？"},{"pid":"73014bf656fe392fd20fb1ef93fb6fa1984f277b","tid":159743,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T10:15:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實有冇可能一邊擰下擰下個鏡頭，一邊用用吸塵機吸走入面d塵呢？<br />\n<br />\n但又要確保唔會有新既塵係鏡頭邊位入返去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗到腦已壞</blockquote><br />\n有無咁多塵呀？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n數碼相機鏡頭用耐都有呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f40ec6fea02e09dca7e1ce821f32eec532c08d3c","tid":159743,"uid":28001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T10:42:46.000Z","msg":"係咪強迫症ja? 幾粒塵成像應該完全無影響"},{"pid":"795793bf22130fa30e463b9d3ba2c6a60dc3bdd2","tid":159743,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T10:47:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪強迫症ja? 幾粒塵成像應該完全無影響</blockquote><br />\n好多塵，十幾年鏡，其實冇野既，不過對住個吸塵機忽然諗有冇可能之嘛。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7300a31066c04f3ddb7f5ad5c15750570b7b5908","tid":159743,"uid":28001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:02:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪強迫症ja? 幾粒塵成像應該完全無影響</blockquote><br />\n好多塵，十幾年鏡，其實冇野既，不過對住個吸塵機忽然諗有冇可能之嘛。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n.鏡有啲塵無野的，cmos 有塵就話姐"},{"pid":"bbd7626e170fa66cdc24acf03abafed62ada7f93","tid":159743,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:36:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係咪強迫症ja? 幾粒塵成像應該完全無影響</blockquote><br />\n好多塵，十幾年鏡，其實冇野既，不過對住個吸塵機忽然諗有冇可能之嘛。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n.鏡有啲塵無野的，cmos 有塵就話姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就算有都有左好耐<br />\n只係諗有冇人用吸塵機去吸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d972e6c2dcaa78de68b979dcebe328fb3987166c","tid":159743,"uid":5277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T14:20:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qy7sA51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQy7sA51.jpg&h=8913b9c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鏡頭形單反吸塵機"},{"pid":"595c1556cf4d00856fc263946b204ca37525f668","tid":159743,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T18:04:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/22CVDZB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F22CVDZB.png&h=c9ddbf7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n只是相機入面吸塵 (定係純粹抽氣?)<br />\n唔係吸鏡頭入面<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n宜家大部分機種CMOS/CCD都有超聲波除塵<br />\n我諗應該冇幾可要用<br />\n至少我影左幾年果架個CMOS都冇我見得到嘅塵"},{"pid":"2ac66de0bfd17345c328384644cd15947a33d227","tid":159743,"uid":80072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T19:59:21.000Z","msg":"我都有諗過，遲d試吓，雖然冇影響但見到堆塵始終有啲唔開胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2edf1bcce09e3f4184fc5794cb9df08c9d768f7c","tid":159743,"uid":3811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T00:33:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qy7sA51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQy7sA51.jpg&h=8913b9c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鏡頭形單反吸塵機</blockquote><br />\n富賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"201db73d66780c60128c674ff93ec72eee1a5df5","tid":159743,"uid":45635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T03:58:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qy7sA51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQy7sA51.jpg&h=8913b9c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鏡頭形單反吸塵機</blockquote><br />\n富賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪某名人出架"}]}